Class IterativeSolver

  • java.lang.Object
    • algo.iterative.IterativeSolver
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ISolver
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    CvCostCapacitySortedSolver, NaiveSolver, RandomSolver
    public class IterativeSolver
extends Object
implements ISolver
    Implementation of a Naive solver. This solver iterates over all clients and try to assign them a vehicule.
    Author:
    Corentin, Lilian Petitpas

      • iterativeSolver

        private void iterativeSolver()
                      throws SolverException
        Solve the current instance using a naive algorithm. It iterates over all clients and try to assign them a vehicule. If it is not possible, ask for an external vehicule.
        Throws:
        SolverException - If there is an internal exception or inconsistant values.
